data.description:
Wow, You'll love this beautiful 5 bedroom 2.5 bath home which is located in the heart of the Glendale Sports and Entertainment District. With restaurants, shopping, movie theaters, casino, groceries, golf, and sports stadium, all within a mile of your next home. This home is in  Rovey Farms Estates with 3 park areas within walking distance. Features include 9 ft. ceilings, A light, bright, open floor plan over 3000 sq. ft.
Downstairs has a large formal living room and a great room (family room/kitchen combo) with a gas range & oven.
The upstairs is split with the large master suite on one side of home and 4 nice sized bedrooms on the other separated by a lg. loft area which can be used as a game room, study, library etc. Large rear yard features several garden areas.  See this home today
